# Product images folder
#
# Naming convention: lowercase product name with spaces replaced by hyphens, .jpg extension.
# Examples:
#   "Classic Burger"  -> classic-burger.jpg
#   "Chicken Breast"  -> chicken-breast.jpg
#   "Coca-Cola"       -> coca-cola.jpg
#
# When a matching file exists here, the POS pages automatically pick it up.
# Otherwise they fall back to a named placeholder image (no code changes needed).
#
# See ProductModel::getProductImagePath() for the exact slug rule.
